**Describe your issue**

Utilities `float-start` and `clear-start` generate this with TW3:

```css
.float-start {
  float: inline-start;
}
.clear-start {
  clear: inline-start;
}
```

and this with TW4:

```css
.float-start {
  float: start;
}
.clear-start {
  clear: start;
}
```

which seem to be "Invalid property value"-s according to Chrome/Firefox dev tools.

